text.tspan: The Islesboro Energy Committee & ICC welcome all community members
to drop by this family-friendly, OUTDOOR event featuring:
▶ Talk to experts in Home Energy Savings, Heating, & Weatherization
Heat Pumps, Insulation, Community and Home Solar & Batteries
▶ See Melissa Jagger's ICS Sustainability Class Projects Showcase
▶ 11am onward: Lunch & Desserts to support the
Energy Experts & Community Members in quick Porch talks
▶ 12-1pm: Live music by Tom, Natasha, & Anne McKee
▶ 1:30-3pm: Electric Car and E-Bike Test Rides
Please bring a mask for all outdoor conversations
Remember your hat, sunscreen, and water bottle!
